            "title": "Benefits of In-Ground Hoops",
            "desc": "<h3>Long-Term Results </h3><p>We pride ourselves on quality at <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/\">Fenceworks</a>, and this means partnering with a leader like PROformance Hoops. With thick tempered glass on the backboard and a galvanized steel pole, your investment will survive the weather and offer fun for the family for many years to come. </p><h3>Stability and Strength </h3><p>Your in-ground hoop is set in concrete, which prevents tipping, wobbling, shaking, and other movement. In a commercial setting where competitive play is common, this stability is invaluable. </p><h3>Professional Appearance </h3><p>Whether residential or commercial, you might seek that professional feel, and it comes with in-ground options. With 72-, 54-, and 60-inch basketball hoops in-ground, you can tailor your choice to your needs, and the hoop will look professional both now and in the future.</p><h3>Theft Protection </h3><p>If you’re tired of your portable hoop being a target of theft, or blowing over in the wind, it could be time for an upgrade. <br/></p>",
