            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "Why Choose Fenceworks for In-Ground Basketball Hoops?",
            "desc": "<p>Our business was affectionately known as ‘The Guy on 41’ for many years; while we may have moved to a stunning showroom in Northbrook, our small family business feel remains. We strive to provide value for all customers, whether you need fencing, playsets, basketball hoops, or trampolines. Stan Ascher launched the business in the 1960s, and now the second and third generation both work in the business.</p><p>We’re proud of our reputation in the community, and this means we’ll only ever put our name to reliable, quality products. We’ll visit your property, provide tailored advice, and give that personal touch that big box stores and online retailers just can’t offer. If you like to buy products with a touch of old-school customer service, Fenceworks is the place for you. </p><p>Contact our family today to explore in-ground basketball systems and potentially find the one that provides your friends, family, colleagues, and customers with endless fun! </p>",
